                    <div class="accordion-body">You have three options: <strong>1.</strong> Subscribe to Pro Monthly ($3.99/month) — flexible, cancel anytime. <strong>2.</strong> Unlock Pro Lifetime ($9.99 launch pricing) — one payment, Pro forever. <strong>3.</strong> Keep the free tier — your earliest alarm stays fully functional with playback, snooze, and dismiss. Additional alarms and Pro features are disabled. You won't lose your alarm configurations. If you upgrade later, everything is restored.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq16" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq16">
                        What's the difference between Monthly and Lifetime?
                    </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq16" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">Both unlock the exact same Pro features. Monthly renews at $3.99/month and can be canceled anytime through Google Play. Lifetime is a single $9.99 payment that permanently unlocks Pro — the current price is our Founding Member launch rate, and it's expected to increase over time.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq17" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq17">
                        Can I switch from Monthly to Lifetime?
                    </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq17" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">Yes. You can purchase Lifetime at any time. After buying Lifetime, cancel your monthly subscription in Google Play to stop future charges. Your Pro access continues permanently through the Lifetime unlock.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h3 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq18" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq18">
                        Can I restore my purchase on a new device?
                    </button>
                </h3>
                <div id="faq18" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">Yes. Open the app, go to Settings, and tap &quot;Restore Purchases.&quot; Lifetime purchases and active subscriptions are restored through your Google Play account.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

